
1. create Context
context=createContext(null)
   its has provider ~ its provide the data
    and consumer ~ its consume the data

2. wrap out components in provider

<context.Provider value={user}>
childer
</context.Provider>

3. consume the value with help of consumer

<context.Consumer>
        {
        (value)=>(
           <div>
             {value.name}
           </div>
            )
        }


</context.Consumer>
